{"tid":937693,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人對傷心事個反應好慢","createTime":"2018-12-11T17:42:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T15:11:34.000Z","uid":138731,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e032193162d3d9695b2d7dc88b38be31db3f4302","tid":937693,"uid":138731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T17:42:33.000Z","msg":"我成日對啲傷心既事都反應得好慢 例如 比最好既朋友出賣 中意既男仔當我好朋友咁捉住我講呢排溝緊咩女<br />\n我當下通常都係覺得無乜野 <br />\n過左一日兩日 嗰啲傷心先珊珊來遲咁湧出黎 <br />\n傷心到坐立不安 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人都係咁 定係純粹係我反應慢<br />\n呢排又發生左事 我呢一刻咩感覺都無<br />\n好怕過兩日訓醒會傷心"},{"pid":"a7039d234157d823ef0faeb59ea67b4e68270f30","tid":937693,"uid":138731,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T17:46:14.000Z","msg":"講開又講 前排個男仔又搵我傾佢啲女 但我已經下定左決心唔會再中意佢 我傷傷下心 忽然意識到我其實都唔中意佢啦 有咩好傷心 <br />\n就突然有一秒好似有人將唔開心由我個腦抽走左咁<br />\n好突兀好奇怪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能係外星人吸走左啲能量"},{"pid":"11381bc6b9eefb70f9f72f7232543d0af5f956e8","tid":937693,"uid":57185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T17:47:31.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4370343bcc6e01eceb5edeb144811e10559ba8","tid":937693,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T17:57:58.000Z","msg":"我都係<br />\n可以過左幾日諗多左野所以先有反應"},{"pid":"a62d0d96cb325d86d7a51616cfdf0d816cbd0ed2","tid":937693,"uid":138731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11381bc6b9eefb70f9f72f7232543d0af5f956e8","tid":937693,"uid":57185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T17:47:31.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T17:59:45.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過啲科學啲既解釋<br />\n我有思考過係咪件事對我打擊太大 所以聽到嗰下個腦proces